name: ROYAL CANIN Chihuahua Adult
description: Diet is a very important factor in supporting the health of your adult Chihuahua. ROYAL CANIN Chihuahua Adult is suitable for Chihuahuas aged 8 months and over. The food has been specially tailored to the needs of adult Chihuahuas, who are considered very picky.

name: ROYAL CANIN BHN Yorkshire Terrier Adult
description: Yorkshire Terriers, or Yorkies, are balanced, active and intelligent dogs full of energy and enthusiasm. The little terrier is eager to learn, playful and self-confident. Every breed of dog has different needs. Diet should take this into account to support optimal health. ROYAL CANIN Yorkshire Terrier Adult is suitable for Yorkshire Terriers from 10 months and has been specially tailored to the nutritional needs of this breed.

name: ROYAL CANIN MEDIUM Adult dry food for medium-sized dogs
description: At 12 months, a medium-sized dog is fully grown, although his behavior may seem like that of a puppy for a while. Good nutrition is just as important at this stage of life as it is during growth. Ensuring that food provides the right nutrients in the right amounts is key to supporting and maintaining health. ROYAL CANIN Medium Adult is specifically tailored to the nutritional needs of a medium-sized, adult dog. The food is ideal for dogs aged 1-7 years with a body weight of 11kg-25kg.

name: ROYAL CANIN MAXI Adult dry food for large dogs
description: The nutritional needs of large dogs differ enormously from the needs of smaller dogs. It is therefore particularly important to ensure a balanced diet that is tailored to the dog's specific needs, which depend on size and age. The ROYAL CANIN Maxi Adult dog food is specially tailored to the needs of your dog. It is suitable for large dogs from 15 months of age and weighing 26kg-44kg when fully grown.

name: ROYAL CANIN MINI Adult dry food for small dogs
description: Even when a dog becomes an adult, it is important to ensure that their diet continues to provide the important nutrients that support optimal health throughout adulthood. ROYAL CANIN Mini Adult is suitable for small dogs from 10 months and weighing up to 10 kg and has been specially tailored to the needs of small dogs.

name: ROYAL CANIN Labrador Retriever Adult Sterilized dry food for neutered dogs
description: The lovable, lively and good-natured Labrador Retriever is both a popular family pet and a versatile companion dog. Thanks to its agility, intelligence and keen sense of smell, the Labrador Retriever is often used as a guide dog or search and rescue dog. Nutrition is also an essential component of a healthy life for neutered, adult Labradors. For this reason, choosing a balanced diet is very important.

name: ROYAL CANIN MINI Adult 8+ dry food for older small dogs

ROYAL CANIN Mini Adult 8+ is suitable for small dogs aged 8 and over weighing up to 10 kg and has been specially tailored to the needs of small, adult dogs

name: ROYAL CANIN Dachshund Adult dry dog ​​food for Dachshunds

Because each dog breed has its own unique needs, nutrition should support their unique lifestyle and promote optimal health. ROYAL CANIN Dachshund Adult is suitable for dachshunds from 10 months of age and has been specially adapted to the needs of adult dachshunds.
